SOCCER - FORMER ROMANIA COACH RETURNS TO UNIVERSITATEA . Ex - Romania soccer trainer Mircea Radulescu has been appointed coach of his former first division club Universitatea Craiova , club officials said on Monday . " We are glad to announce Radulescu ' s appointement and we hope to put the bad results of 1996 behind as soon as possible , " said Universitatea vice - president Marcel Popescu , whose side finished near the bottom of the table last season . Radulescu , who replaces Emeric Jenei , coached Craiova from 1984 - 86 and the Romanian national side from 1992 - 93 . Jenei left when he was appointed deputy sports minister late last year after four months in charge at Universitatea . 
